metadata.name: Zaisha - Desi “that girl”
metadata.description: Zaisha is an Indian millennial who, like many women in present era, is a multitasker. She's a social media manager at a startup who enjoys makeup and is known for her sleek demeanour. Zaisha enjoys going to the gym and investing in NFTs. She has a creative soul and enjoys singing, dancing, and creating beautiful acrylic artwork. Despite having a stable life, she still feels insecure about her body and her future. Nonetheless, this does not prevent her from doing what she want.
